= 1979, In the Dragon's den

{!<div class="typewriter dialogue2" id="dialogue2">!}

As the years sharpened you, Alfred was always by your side to guide you into a much better man than you would have been without him.

You eventually found that if anything ought to change, you had to emancipate from him to fight for justice.

As training continued, words reached you from a strange group fighting corruption in the Himalayas. 

They had seen much potential in you and gave you the opportunity to finally have the tools necessary to push the change you wanted to see.

You only had to prove yourself against one of them.

{!</div>!}

- @intro_david: You trained with the arm of the demon
- @intro_talia: You trained with daughter of the demon
- @intro_shiva: You trained with the voice of the demon


